                    <td>Pass an XML fragment through an XSLT identity transformation.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <a href="examples/twitter.xproc" target="_example">twitter.xproc [<a href="examples/twitter.xproc?debug=1" target="_example">debug</a>]</a>
